trans-unit.source: Defines configuration settings that are used to support the compilation infrastructure of Web applications.
trans-unit.target: Definerer konfigurasjonsinnstillinger som brukes til å støtte kompilering infrastrukturen til webprogrammer.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The CompilationSection class provides a way to programmatically access and modify the content of the `compilation` section of the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Klassen CompilationSection gjør det mulig å programmatisk tilgang til og endre innholdet i den `compilation` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"></xref> class by using default settings.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av standardinnstillingene.

trans-unit.source: The CompilationSection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren CompilationSection skal ikke brukes direkte fra koden.

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
trans-unit.target: Kalles av ASP.NET Konfigurasjonssystemet.

trans-unit.source: You can obtain an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection> class by using the <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du kan få en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection>klassen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: This property contains the assembly references to use during compilation of a dynamic ASP.NET resource.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen inneholder samlingen referansene skal brukes under kompilering av en dynamisk ASP.NET-ressurs.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET automatically links these assemblies to the resource when compiling each code module.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET kobler automatisk disse samlingene til ressursen ved kompilering av hver code-modul.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"></xref> that contains the assembly objects used during compilation of an ASP.NET resource.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.AssemblyCollection"> </xref> som inneholder samlingen objektene som brukes under kompilering av en ASP.NET-ressurs.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value specifying a post-process compilation step for an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir et etter behandle kompilering trinn for en samling.

trans-unit.source: A string value specifying the post-process compilation step for an assembly.
trans-unit.target: En strengverdi som angir etter behandle kompilering trinn for en samling.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether batch compilation is attempted.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om bunkekompilering forsøk.

trans-unit.source: Set this attribute to `true` to change the delay caused by the required compilation when you access an uncompiled file.
trans-unit.target: Angi dette attributtet til `true` endre forsinkelsen skyldes nødvendige kompileringen når du kobler til en ukompilert fil.

trans-unit.source: Setting this attribute to `true` instructs ASP.NET to precompile all the uncompiled files in batch mode.
trans-unit.target: Angivelse av dette attributtet `true` angir at ASP.NET å forhåndskompilere alle ukompilert filene i satsvis modus.

trans-unit.source: A delay occurs when the files are first compiled; however once the files are compiled, the delay is eliminated.
trans-unit.target: En forsinkelse oppstår når filene først kompileres; imidlertid når filene er kompilert, forsinkelsen er fjernet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if batch compilation is attempted; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis du vil bli forsøkt bunkekompilering. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the time-out period, in seconds, for batch compilation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir tidsavbruddsperioden i sekunder for bunkekompilering.

trans-unit.source: Indicates the time-out period, in seconds, for batch compilation.
trans-unit.target: Angir tidsavbruddsperioden i sekunder for bunkekompilering.

trans-unit.source: If the compilation cannot be completed within the time-out period, the compiler reverts to single-compilation mode for the current page.
trans-unit.target: Hvis kompilering ikke kan fullføres innen tidsavbruddsperioden, tilbakestilles kompilatoren til enkel Kompileringsmodus for gjeldende side.

trans-unit.source: A value indicating the amount of time in seconds granted for batch compilation to occur.
trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir hvor lang tid i sekunder gitt for bunkekompilering kan utføres.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"></xref> collection of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"> </xref> samling av <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider> object provides the functionality to parse a specific file type and to generate code from that file.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider>objektet inneholder funksjonaliteten til å analysere en bestemt filtype, og til å generere kode fra filen.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.BuildProvider>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"></xref> that contains the build providers used during a compilation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BuildProviderCollection"> </xref> som inneholder build-leverandører som brukes under en kompilering.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CodeSubDirectoriesCollection"></xref> of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CodeSubDirectoriesCollection"></xref> of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: This property defines an ordered collection of subdirectories containing files compiled at run time.
trans-unit.target: Definerer en sortert samling av undermapper som inneholder filer som er kompilert ved kjøretid.

trans-unit.source: There can be any number of subdirectories.
trans-unit.target: Det kan være et tall for undermapper med.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CodeSubDirectoriesCollection"></xref> collection that contains an ordered collection of subdirectories containing files compiled at run time.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CodeSubDirectoriesCollection"> </xref> samlingen som inneholder en sortert samling av undermapper som inneholder filer som er kompilert ved kjøretid.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"></xref> collection of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"> </xref> samling av <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The Compilers property does not refer to any actual element in the underlying configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen kompilatorer refererer ikke til noen faktiske element i underliggende konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: It is a construct that allows easy access to the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.Compiler> objects it contains.
trans-unit.target: Det er en konstruksjon som gir enkel tilgang til den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.Compiler>objekter den inneholder.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.Compiler>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"></xref> collection that contains a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"> </xref> samlingen som inneholder en samling av <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a string representing the object type used to intercept a <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"></xref> object and configure a container.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en streng som representerer objekttypen brukes til å fange opp en <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"> </xref> objekt og Konfigurer en beholder.

trans-unit.source: A string representing the object type used to intercept a <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: En streng som representerer objekttypen brukes til å fange opp en <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value specifying whether to compile release binaries or debug binaries.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om du vil kompilere utgaven binærfiler eller feilsøke binærfiler.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if debug binaries will be used for compilation; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis feilsøking binærfiler skal brukes for å utføre kompilering; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> specifies that release binaries will be used for compilation.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>Angir at versjonen binærfiler brukes for å utføre kompilering.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the default programming language to use in dynamic-compilation files.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir standard programmeringsspråk som skal brukes i dynamiske kompileringsfiler.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the default programming language, such as C# or VB.NET, to use in dynamic compilation files.
trans-unit.target: Angir standard programmeringsspråk, for eksempel C# eller VB.NET, skal brukes i dynamiske kompileringsfiler.

trans-unit.source: Language names are defined using the `system.codedom` section.
trans-unit.target: Språknavn er definert ved hjelp av `system.codedom` delen.

trans-unit.source: The default programming language is `vb`, which specifies VB.NET as the default programming language.
trans-unit.target: Standard programmeringsspråk er `vb`, som angir VB.NET som standard programmeringsspråk.

trans-unit.source: A value specifying the default programming language to use in dynamic-compilation files.
trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir standard programmeringsspråk som skal brukes i dynamiske kompileringsfiler.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether the "disableObsoleteWarnings" configuration value in the Compilation section is set.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir om verdien for "disableObsoleteWarnings"-konfigurasjonen under kompilering er angitt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the "disableObsoleteWarnings" configuration value in the Compilation section is set; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis "disableObsoleteWarnings" konfigurasjonsverdien under kompilering er angitt; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether an ASP.NET application can take advantage of [!INCLUDE[win8](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] prefetch functionality.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om en ASP.NET-programmet kan dra nytte av [!INCLUDE[win8](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] forhåndshenting funksjonalitet.

trans-unit.source: Prefetch is a utility that is intended to improve application startup performance by loading application data into memory before it is demanded .
trans-unit.target: Forhåndshentingstjenesten er et verktøy som er ment å forbedre ytelsen for programmet startet av programdata lastes inn i minnet før den er etterspørsel etter.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The [!INCLUDE[win8](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] prefetch service must be configured and running for this setting to be effective.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den [!INCLUDE[win8](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] forhåndshentingstjenesten tjenesten må være konfigurert og kjøre for denne innstillingen skal fungere.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if an ASP.NET application can take advantage of [!INCLUDE[win8](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] prefetch functionality; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis en ASP.NET-programmet kan dra nytte av [!INCLUDE[win8](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] forhåndshenting funksjonalitet; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether to use the Microsoft Visual Basic <xref uid="langword_csharp_explicit" name="explicit" href=""></xref> compile option.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om du vil bruke Microsoft Visual Basic <xref uid="langword_csharp_explicit" name="explicit" href=""> </xref> kompileres alternativet.

trans-unit.source: This property specifies the setting of the Microsoft Visual Basic `explicit` compile option.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir innstillingen for Microsoft Visual Basic `explicit` kompileres alternativet.

trans-unit.source: When set to `true`, the Visual Basic `explicit` compile option is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du velger `true`, Visual Basic `explicit` kompilering-alternativet er aktivert.

trans-unit.source: When the option is enabled, all variables must be explicitly declared using a `Dim`, `Private`, `Public`, or `ReDim` statement.
trans-unit.target: Når alternativet er aktivert, alle variabler må deklareres eksplisitt ved hjelp av en `Dim`, `Private`, `Public`, eller `ReDim` setningen.

trans-unit.source: The default is `true`.
trans-unit.target: Standard `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the Visual Basic <xref uid="langword_csharp_explicit" name="explicit" href=""></xref> compile option is enabled; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis Visual Basic <xref uid="langword_csharp_explicit" name="explicit" href=""> </xref> kompilering-alternativet er aktivert, ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> specifies that the Visual Basic <xref uid="langword_csharp_explicit" name="explicit" href=""></xref> compile option is disabled.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>Angir at Visual Basic <xref uid="langword_csharp_explicit" name="explicit" href=""> </xref> alternativet kompilering er deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProviderCollection"> </xref> samling av <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilationSection"> </xref> klassen som representerer build-leverandører som brukes under kompilering.

trans-unit.target: Build-leverandører som brukes under kompilering.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den maksimale kombinerte størrelsen for de genererte kildefilene per bunkekompilering.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the maximum size (in kilobytes) of the generated source files per batched compilation.
trans-unit.target: Angir den maksimale størrelsen (i kilobyte) for de genererte kildefilene per bunkekompilering.

trans-unit.source: The default value is 1000 KB.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 1000 KB.

trans-unit.source: An integer value indicating the maximum combined size of the generated source files per batched compilation.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir den maksimale kombinerte størrelsen for de genererte kildefilene per bunkekompilering.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the maximum number of pages per batched compilation.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir det maksimale antallet sider per bunkekompilering.

trans-unit.source: An integer value indicating the maximum number of pages that will be compiled into a single batch.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som angir det maksimale antallet sider kompileres til et enkelt satsvis.

trans-unit.source: The default number of pages is 1000.
trans-unit.target: Standardantallet sider er 1000.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the number of dynamic recompiles of resources that can occur before the application restarts.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir antallet dynamiske nye kompileringer for ressurser som kan forekomme før applikasjonen startes på nytt.

trans-unit.source: Indicates the number of dynamic recompiles of resources that can occur before the application restarts.
trans-unit.target: Angir antallet dynamiske nye kompileringer for ressurser som kan forekomme før applikasjonen startes på nytt.

trans-unit.source: This attribute is supported at the global and application configuration levels, but not at the directory configuration level.
trans-unit.target: Dette attributtet støttes på de globale og programmet konfigurasjonsnivåer, men ikke på nivå directory konfigurasjon.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > ASP.NET increases the NumRecompilesBeforeAppRestart property value every time an assembly is invalidated and fails to be deleted.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > ASP.NET øker egenskapsverdien NumRecompilesBeforeAppRestart hver gang en samling er ugyldig og ikke kan slettes.

trans-unit.source: A value indicating the number of dynamic recompiles of resources that can occur before the application restarts.
trans-unit.target: En verdi som angir antallet dynamiske nye kompileringer for ressurser som kan forekomme før applikasjonen startes på nytt.

trans-unit.source: The default is 15 recompilations.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er 15 kompileringer.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the compilation must be optimized.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om kompileringen må optimalisert.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the compilation must be optimized; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis kompileringen må optimaliseres; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether the application is optimized for the deployed environment.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om programmet er optimalisert for distribuert miljøet.

trans-unit.source: When this property is set to <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGuidedOptimizationsFlags>, the ASP.NET compilation system enables optimizations that are intended to speed up ASP.NET startup performance at the expense of increased CPU utilization.
trans-unit.target: Når denne egenskapen er satt til <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGuidedOptimizationsFlags>, ASP.NET kompilering systemet aktiverer profileringsoptimaliseringer som er ment å øke hastigheten på ASP.NET startet ytelsen på bekostning av større prosessorbruken.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGuidedOptimizationsFlags>

trans-unit.source: The default setting for this property is <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGuidedOptimizationsFlags>.
trans-unit.target: Standardinnstillingen for denne egenskapen er <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGuidedOptimizationsFlags>.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfileGuidedOptimizationsFlags>

trans-unit.source: A value that indicates whether the application is optimized for the deployed environment.

trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir Visual Basic <xref uid="langword_csharp_strict" name="strict" href=""> </xref> kompileres alternativet.

trans-unit.source: When `true`, compilation explicitly disallows any data-type conversions in which data loss would occur, and any conversion between numeric types and strings.
trans-unit.target: Når `true`, kompilering eksplisitt tillater ikke flere datatypen konverteringer på hvilke data vil gå tapt, og konvertering mellom numeriske datatyper og strenger.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the Visual Basic <xref uid="langword_csharp_strict" name="strict" href=""></xref> compile option is used; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether instructions to the compiler use physical paths or URLs.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om instruksjoner for kompilatoren bruker fysiske baner eller URL-adresser.

trans-unit.source: If this property is specified as `true` in the configuration, URLs will be used for the compiler instructions instead of physical paths.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne egenskapen er angitt som `true` i konfigurasjonen, URL-adressene som skal brukes for kompilatoren instruksjonene i stedet for fysiske baner.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if instructions to the compiler use URLs rather than physical paths; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis instruksjonene til kompilatoren bruker URL-adresser i stedet for fysisk baner. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
